@EndUserText.label: 'Export Document Header Invoice Report'
@Metadata.allowExtensions: true
@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
define root view entity ZETR_DDL_C_EXP_INV_HEAD_RPT
  provider contract transactional_query
  as projection on ZETR_DDL_I_EXP_INV_HEAD_RPT
{
  key     BillingDocument,
          CompanyCode,
          CompanyCodeName,
          BillingDocumentType,
          BillingDocumentTypeName,
          SalesOrganization,
          SalesOrganizationName,
          DistributionChannel,
          DistributionChannelName,
          Division,
          DivisionName,
          PayerParty,
          PayerPartyName,
          SoldToParty,
          SoldToPartyName,
          kunre,
          kunre_txt,
          TotalNetAmount,
          TotalTaxAmount,
          TransactionCurrency,
          BillingDocumentDate,
          DocumentReferenceID,
          CustomerPaymentTerms,
          CustomerPaymentTermsName,
          IncotermsClassification,
          IncotermsTransferLocation,
          IncotermsVersion,
          CreationDate,
          CreationTime,
          CreatedByUser,
          SDDocumentCategory,
          AccountingTransferStatus,
          AccountingTransferStatusText,
          BillingDocumentIsCancelled,
          CancelledBillingDocument,
          AccountingDocument,
          FiscalYear,
          DocumentNumber,

          @ObjectModel.virtualElementCalculatedBy: 'ABAP:ZCL_ETR_INV_DOC_VIREL'
  virtual DocumentURL : abap.string(0)
}
